metadata.name: Ultraviolet Ranunculus
metadata.description:
Planned Parenthood provides help to women when they need it most.  Through a worldwide network of donors, physicians and caregivers, the organization has created a global community dedicated to keeping women safe and protecting their bodily autonomy. 

This piece was minted in order to raise funds for Planned Parenthood.  The video was created using a custom Ultraviolet photography process to capture fluorescent ink being absorbed through the flower’s petals.  Sound design was provided by Matt Nordstrom.

As Ultraviolet light uncovers a process that is invisible to the human eye, this piece seeks to illuminate the network of supports that help make Planned Parenthood possible. Like the flower’s vascular system, caregivers and donors are able to connect through the organization and reach women in need.  

LICENSING:  Primary NFT holder is free to display privately and in groups as long as Maggie West is credited.  Purchase provides no right to create commercial merchandise, commercial distribution or any derivative works.  Copyright remains with Maggie West.
